可以通过 plugins.readingTime 配置，但不推荐</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">    </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\"><v-menu class=\"twoslash-hover\" popper-class=\"shiki twoslash-floating vp-copy-ignore vp-code\" theme=\"twoslash\"><span>plugins</span><template v-slot:popper=\"&#123;}\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-container vp-copy-ignore\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"twoslash-popup-code\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">ThemeOptions</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">plugins</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">?:</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> ThemeBuiltinPlugins</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> |</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> undefined</span></code><div class=\"twoslash-popup-docs vp-doc\" vp-content=\"\"><p>主题内置插件配置</p>\n<p>请勿将此配置与 <a href=\"https://v2.vuepress.vuejs.org/zh/reference/config.html#plugins\">vuepress plugins</a> 混淆</p></div></span></template></v-menu></span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">: &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">      </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\"><v-menu class=\"twoslash-hover\" popper-class=\"shiki twoslash-floating vp-copy-ignore vp-code\" theme=\"twoslash\"><span>readingTime</span><template v-slot:popper=\"&#123;}\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-container vp-copy-ignore\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"twoslash-popup-code\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">ThemeBuiltinPlugins</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">readingTime</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB59